name: Project Kaze Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct ship hulls related to the secretive "Project Kaze".

name: Kassadari Equipment Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the arcane weapon and fighter designs of the Great Houses of Kassadar.

name: Kassadari Database Backup
desc: A long-lost backup of a Kassadari datavault, containing schematics to all the designs of the Great Houses of Kassadar.

name: Legio Infernalis Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the obscure weapon and fighter designs of the Legio Infernalis.

name: Legio Infernalis Full Database
desc: A database containing all ship and weapon designs of the Legio Infernalis as provided only to its most loyal members.

name: Lifeless Project Database
desc: The remains of a hidden database, recovered from a secret data vault. It contains schematics to what is referred to as the Lifeless Fleet.

name: Mysterious Blueprint Archive
desc: A blueprint archive of unknown origins. It appears to contain a massive collection of rare blueprints from all corners of the sector.
